00:14.202 --> 00:16.085
So...

00:16.085 --> 00:17.938
what did you think?

00:17.939 --> 00:19.156
Well, who knew

00:19.157 --> 00:22.225
that beef lollipop
and foie gras mousse and mint

00:22.226 --> 00:23.643
could be so delicious.

00:23.644 --> 00:26.146
You're making fun of me.

00:26.147 --> 00:27.764
No, I loved it.

00:27.765 --> 00:30.000
Now I see why it's so hard
to get in this place.

00:33.621 --> 00:36.406
I had the best day
today, Maggie.

00:36.407 --> 00:39.042
You should see your face
right now-- you're beaming.

00:39.043 --> 00:40.544
It's all the sun we got

00:40.545 --> 00:42.212
on the water taxi
to Battery Park.

00:42.213 --> 00:43.947
I gotta say, the
Statue of Liberty

00:43.948 --> 00:45.715
from that
perspective...

00:45.716 --> 00:47.250
really was something.

00:47.251 --> 00:49.219
Yeah.
Guys?

00:49.220 --> 00:50.420
Excuse me,
I hate to interrupt

00:50.421 --> 00:52.022
but they want me
to close out for the night.

00:52.023 --> 00:54.174
Oh sure. You need us
to settle up? No problem.

00:54.175 --> 00:55.792
How was everything?
Fantastic.

00:55.793 --> 00:58.127
My wife kept telling me,

00:58.128 --> 01:00.230
Iowa's got nothing like this.

01:00.231 --> 01:02.199
That's the state
that grows all the corn?

01:02.200 --> 01:03.667
Or is it potatoes?

01:03.668 --> 01:05.235
Oh, corn.

01:05.236 --> 01:07.804
Though most of what I grow now
is turned into biofuel.

01:07.805 --> 01:09.272
Ethanol.

01:09.273 --> 01:11.524
It's a renewable
energy source.

01:11.525 --> 01:13.643
My husband loves his work.

01:13.644 --> 01:14.744
Cool.

01:14.745 --> 01:16.680
Well, listen,
enjoy the rest of your trip.

01:16.681 --> 01:18.481
For you.

01:18.482 --> 01:20.951
Thank you.

01:20.952 --> 01:23.086
You sure I can't get you
anything else before I go?

01:23.087 --> 01:24.955
No, we're fine.
I am just

01:24.956 --> 01:27.824
going to go and have
my after dinner cigar.

01:27.825 --> 01:30.193
But not right
outside, okay?

01:30.194 --> 01:32.495
Um, smoke gets in:
customers hate it.

01:32.496 --> 01:35.515
But a little ways down
to the left is cool.

01:38.569 --> 01:41.771
I'll be back before
you finish your sambuca.

01:48.579 --> 01:50.897
Hey. Sorry I'm late.

01:51.949 --> 01:54.901
Well, you said you were
running a half-hour behind,

01:54.902 --> 01:56.903
so that makes you on time.

01:58.456 --> 02:00.090
Long day?

02:00.091 --> 02:03.493
Some eight-hour days
feel like a week.

02:03.494 --> 02:05.762
Yeah.

02:05.763 --> 02:07.764
Anything you want to unload?

02:08.666 --> 02:10.166
How are you?

02:10.167 --> 02:12.402
Me?

02:12.403 --> 02:14.037
Well, I'm headed
for another run-in

02:14.038 --> 02:15.105
with the Port Authority...

02:15.106 --> 02:17.540
Ian Boyd was shot dead today.

02:17.541 --> 02:19.542
Good. Who shot him?

02:19.543 --> 02:22.646
A convenience store owner
he was trying to rob,

02:22.647 --> 02:24.898
but not before he was...

02:24.899 --> 02:29.552
able to kill a young woman
who was also in the store.

02:29.553 --> 02:32.889
She was trying to warn the owner
she saw a gun.

02:32.890 --> 02:34.724
Ian shot her.

02:34.725 --> 02:36.726
She was pronounced dead
at the scene.

02:36.727 --> 02:39.229
I'm sorry.

02:40.364 --> 02:43.533
He should have been behind bars
from the last robbery.

02:43.534 --> 02:44.934
That was a jury's decision.

02:44.935 --> 02:47.771
Yeah, on a case that I lost.

02:47.772 --> 02:50.540
And because I lost it, he
was back on the streets,

02:50.541 --> 02:52.509
and because of that,
a young woman is dead.

02:52.510 --> 02:54.110
You can't tell me

02:54.111 --> 02:57.080
I don't bear
some responsibility for that.

02:57.915 --> 03:00.050
Okay.

03:02.453 --> 03:04.387
Menus or another round?

03:05.389 --> 03:07.457
Both.

03:23.207 --> 03:25.442
Did you try the monkfish?
I wanted to.

03:25.443 --> 03:26.643
It all sounded good.

03:26.644 --> 03:27.911
I had the bay
scallops...

03:29.947 --> 03:31.848
What was that?

03:31.849 --> 03:33.282
MAN 2:
Those were gunshots.

03:33.283 --> 03:34.918
They had to be.

03:34.919 --> 03:37.020
What's going on?

03:40.624 --> 03:42.458
Oh, God! Lance, no!

03:42.459 --> 03:43.893
No!

03:43.894 --> 03:46.629
Call 911!

03:46.630 --> 03:49.632
Hurry! My husband's been shot!

